.TH "freezer_change_state" 9 "freezer_change_state" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
freezer_change_state \- change the freezing state of a cgroup_freezer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" freezer_change_state
.BI "(struct freezer *freezer "  ","
.BI "bool freeze "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "freezer" 12
freezer of interest
.IP "freeze" 12
whether to freeze or thaw
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Freeze or thaw \fIfreezer\fP according to \fIfreeze\fP.  The operations are
recursive - all descendants of \fIfreezer\fP will be affected.
